  <h1>Privacy Policy – MoNi</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>MoNi is a personal income and expense tracking app. We respect your privacy. No account, login, or registration is required to use the app.</p>

  <h2>Data Collection</h2>
  <p>MoNi does not collect, transmit, or share any personal data. All transaction records you enter are stored locally on your device and never leave it.</p>

  <h2>Permissions</h2>
  <p>MoNi does not request access to your camera, microphone, location, or contacts.</p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>MoNi uses Google AdMob to display ads. AdMob may collect certain device information and use cookies or similar technologies to serve personalized ads. This data is collected and processed by Google in accordance with their privacy policy. For more information, visit <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>MoNi is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy-related questions: <a href="mailto:info@ledapremium.com">info@ledapremium.com</a></p>

